snippet: The redshirt freshman quarterback Jameis Winston passed for 356 yards and 4 touchdowns in a spectacular debut and No. 11 Florida State dominated Pittsburgh, 41-13, on Monday night.
abstract: Florida State defeats Pittsburgh, 41-13, in college football.
